text: Étalans is a commune. It is in Bourgogne-Franche-Comté in the Doubs department in east France. On 1 January 2017, the former communes of Charbonnières-les- Sapins and Verrières-du-Grosbois were merged into Étalans.Arrêté préfectoral 12 August 2016 == References == Category:Communes in Doubs
title: Étalans
